{"tid":287002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"ToNick開騷　恆仔借機向女友譚杏藍示愛","createTime":"2017-06-17T05:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T15:34:05.000Z","uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2214166cf643efe7dbfec1316b71d4e3fb3a009","tid":287002,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:43:09.000Z","msg":"樂隊ToNick到九展Music Zone舉行音樂會，主音恆仔的父母和女友譚杏藍（小花）亦有到場，小花更在場邊擔任攝影師。ToNick唱出《發你個夢》及《趕客》等歌曲，恆仔坦言早前忙於拍戲，已很久沒開騷，又感觸說：「諗都冇諗過可以夾咁耐Band，可以捱過每一關，開騷可以見到咁多人，希望大家都做多啲諗都冇諗過嘅事。」唱《Go 4OR It》時，恆仔跳向觀眾大玩插水，全場氣氛高漲！Encore時，ToNick向台前幕後致謝，恆仔更特別多謝父母及女友：「有個人冇多謝會死，我哋兩個人喺低潮嘅時候相識，佢話佢想唱歌，我話我都想，我哋互相鼓勵對方，條路未完嘅，好希望可以一路同佢行落去。」 <br />\n<br />\n騷後受訪時，ToNick表示開一場很不夠喉，覺得時間過得很快，成員Ryan說：「真係好好玩，好開心同觀眾好多交流，好多位一齊玩。」恆仔指音樂上儲了很多想法，想爆發出來：「一定要有個機會，玩一個更長嘅騷。下次就未講得住，但已經有計劃，希望年尾可以嚟一次大gathering。」提到大家很喜歡電影《救殭清道夫》的主題曲《長相廝守》，恆仔坦言因此翻唱了幾首電影歌曲，成員晨曦謂：「揀嗰時冇爭拗，因為都係我哋唱K會唱嘅Song List，但真係要揀，因為我哋好多快歌、慢歌都好鍾意Cover，揀真係困難，首首都咁好聽，就即管揀一首自己Handle到嘅，我講我獨唱嗰首。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於獲小花撐足全場，恆仔直言很開心和衷心感謝對方：「好耐之前有個承諾，大家喺音樂上要做啲成績出嚟，希望快啲見到佢都可以喺音樂路上有突破。（喺台上發表愛的宣言？）係愛嘅，但宣言我覺得可以再肉麻啲，諗吓點樣講先。（唔記得多謝佢真係會死？）<span style=\"color: red;\">半死啦，死唔晒，點都留番半條人命喺度</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource :<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170617/mobile/bkn-20170617010419111-0617_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170617%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170617010419111-0617_00862_001.html&d=zF5N07SEFEQhvcktlVjqPkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b519bc58\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170617/mobile/bkn-20170617010419111-0617_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恆仔又比亞視暗星食住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恆仔肯定係俾人迫住多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbd9105f4d6d3e973c0e87001058238d4e8dc1b","tid":287002,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a29e3ea6209e92f56c21d9bd569ef4b1b6d68b","tid":287002,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8f4a3d61c3467d644c6a96909a96fb4b206a8a","tid":287002,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3a111782daf6f1c83c6e1411359af1179ae05d","tid":287002,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47371f50a901377fc13537fc406655ffdeaf1be1","tid":287002,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bbe973abc82202e9e7d990484f3059df7df893b","tid":287002,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜水呀</blockquote><br />\n話明亞視暗星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e25fc7eaf5ea79b142dedb21e2840512209f63","tid":287002,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}